1. Court judgment texts and metadata
   ----------------------------------
   Source:    AustLII — Australasian Legal Information Institute
   URL:       https://www.austlii.edu.au
   Coverage:  149,016 cases from 9 Australian courts/tribunals (2000–2026)
   Terms:     Subject to AustLII's copyright policy
              <http://www.austlii.edu.au/austlii/copyright.html>
   Use:       Permitted for research, study, and education.
              Bulk commercial redistribution is restricted.

2. LLM-extracted structured fields
   --------------------------------
   Fields:    applicant_name, visa_subclass, hearing_date,
              country_of_origin, is_represented, representative,
              and related normalised attributes.
   Generated via:
              Claude Sonnet (Anthropic) and other LLMs routed through
              the Cloudflare AI Gateway compat endpoint.
   Terms:     Licensed under CC BY 4.0 — see DATA_LICENSE.md §2.

3. Vector embeddings
   ------------------
   Generated via OpenAI text-embedding-3-small and
   Google Gemini embedding-001, accessed through Cloudflare AI Gateway.
   Stored in Supabase PostgreSQL with pgvector HNSW indexing.

